comments.body:
Interestingly this is the 2nd version of the bug on the same function - when added 7 years ago it looked like this:
https://github.com/containers/buildah/blame/a16c3cdd7dbd7588966d9e5eeabdcf8258b0e705/imagebuildah/build.go#L705-L709

```golang
	defer func(dockerfiles ...io.ReadCloser) {
		for _, d := range dockerfiles {
			d.Close()
		}
	}()
```

which also was always called with an empy slice.

I've added tests, which helped surface a 2nd bug.
